{
 "name": "RPlog_Everything_With_Your_Testicles_Alright",
 "title": "Everything With Your Testicles Alright",
 "summary": "In the renovated Council Chambers on Caspar, the Imperium's Imperator Darth Malign delivers a polished policy speech pledging cooperation, autonomy, and military aid to help unaffiliated worlds defend themselves, before the formal address gives way to a tense political mingle. The newly-titled Grand Inquisitor Axel Vichten, miserable with a lavender-dry-cleaning allergy afflicting his groin, draws ridicule from his sister Johanna and an offer of dubious salve from Malign himself, who quips 'Everything with your testicles alright?' Grand Moff Elana Tracer, architect of the gathering alongside Crestian Tarasar, works the room to court independent leaders, while the long-vanished ex-Grand Admiral Salin Fawzy and his watchful Falleen companion Ssanyu resurface to settle old scores. When Axel rudely orders Ssanyu to fetch him a drink, she retaliates by publicly squeezing his injured anatomy until he apologizes, much to the amusement of the assembled dignitaries. Malign subtly menaces Fawzy over the Corporate Sector's defection to the Republic before taking his leave, and as the crowd thins and the Wookiee Councillor Zaalbacca unsubtly orders everyone out, Tracer leads the survivors off toward late-night nerf burgers in Plaxton.",
